    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the balance thing but you said \"the immediate focus needs to be on fiscal responsibility\". isnt that basically saying debt reduction is more important than social spending if you have to choose? like, why is debt the \"immediate\" priority instead of, say, making sure people don't starve or lose healthcare?",
